name: Paint Me Like Your Tungsten Girls
description:
Meme created by @defistalker

This piece is the twentieth meme by TungstenDAO, an experimental meme incubation studio.

TungstenDAO will amass a collection of assets that are highly memeable, then create content that reinforces their social significance and strengthens memetic desires for these assets.

Drawing inspiration from NounsDAO, all holders of memes minted by TungstenDAO are members of TungstenDAO, 1 meme = 1 vote.

Governance is currently coordinated via a members only Telegram channel.

The treasury is controlled via governance by holders of memes minted by TungstenDAO.
